author: doe
title: Scoundrels and Bounty Hunter
review:
For the last five years this set has been a total mystery to me but today I am very happy to share some more info on this rare set.

The box is not sealed in the traditional way. It can be opened via a flap that is held in place by a magnet. There are three spaces inside for Han Solo, Chewbacca and Boba Fett. Han and Chewie are glued and in the box. The parts and instructions for Boba Fett come in an additional Zip Lock bag.

You can view additional photos and the instructions on my Flickr Album:

https://www.flickr.com/photos/107326588@N06/albums/72157669048070925
